          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/mikamikamika/" class=" " title="hoBo">hoBo</a>
                (geek)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="15848349">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">我们从出生开始就是无助的，一旦充分认识到这一点，孤独感就会随之而来</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-12-17 00:22</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                我们从出生开始就是无助的，一旦充分认识到这一点，孤独感就会随之而来
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
